Define greeting with name:
    Say "Hello, " + name + "!"
    Say "Nice to meet you!"

Define add_numbers with a, b:
    Let result be a + b
    Say "The sum of " + a + " and " + b + " is " + result

Define check_age with age:
    If age greater than 18 then:
        Say "You are an adult"
    Else:
        Say "You are a minor"

Call greeting with "World"
Call greeting with "Alice"

Call add_numbers with 5, 3
Call add_numbers with 10, 25

Call check_age with 25
Call check_age with 16
